title: Todd and Paul (Everyday Driver)
description: Todd and Paul of Everyday Driver stop by to talk about Guinness records, tranny fluid, BMW 1 series M vs M3, the Fisker Karma, heavy duty pickup trucks, Corvettes, CKY, and the reliability of high end cars.
